Package gov.nasa.larcfm.IO

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigReader
    This object will read in and store a set of configuration parameters.
    SeparatedInput
    A class to parse files with input that are in columns separated by commas, spaces, or tabs.
    SeparatedOutput
    A class to writes a separated value file (separated by commas, spaces, or tabs).
    SequenceReader
    This reads in and stores a set of aircraft states, possibly over time, (and parameters) from a file The Aircraft states are stored in an ArrayList<AircraftState>.
    StateReader
    This reads in and stores a set of aircraft states, possibly over time, (and parameters) from a file The aircraft states are stored in an ArrayList<AircraftState>.
    StateWriter
    This object writes a set of aircraft states, possibly over time, (and parameters) from a file The Aircraft states are stored in an ArrayList.
